text: Red carpets are anything but boring. Like the outrageous characters they portrayed on the silver screen, these celebrities' fashion choices made us do a double (and sometimes a triple) take. For better or worse, these outfits earned some of our favorite stars a slot in our roundup of the most memorable at the Primetime Emmy Awards. While you're at it, don't forget to check out our breakdown of the most talked about Oscars dresses of all time.
